      "message": "Hmm, using non-zero default value is sometimes tricky - we have to be careful not to access CustomGracePeriod directly.\n\nI rather recommend setting the field in all struct initialization. I know there are plenty of them in unit tests, but I guess it\u0027s less error-prone. WDYT?",
